WEBVTT

00:08:01.489 --> 00:08:05.000
But for them, the truth was dangerous.

00:08:06.955 --> 00:08:11.854
By encouraging them to run after it,
I was putting them at risk --

00:08:11.878 --> 00:08:14.235
of persecution,

00:08:14.259 --> 00:08:15.610
of heartbreak.

00:08:18.755 --> 00:08:21.413
When you're not allowed to express
anything in the open,

00:08:21.437 --> 00:08:24.318
you become good at reading
what is unspoken.

00:08:25.736 --> 00:08:30.760
